Usage: setBumpFixed [-help] {-allBumps | -byBumpName {list} | -byBumpSite {list} }

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
-allBumps              # set all bumps fixed (bool, optional)
-byBumpName {list}     # name of bumps to set fixed (string, optional)
-byBumpSite {list}     # name of sites, bump of these site will be set fixed
                       # (string, optional)